<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/930258-i-just-finished-book-1-daughter-of-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I just finished Book 1, Daughter of the Forest, and have a spoilery question pertaining to Finbar and the rest of the series: Do we ever learn what happened to him after he disappeared at the end of Book 1? He was one of my favorite characters and his 'journey' was said to just be starting. I don't wish to know what happened to him, only in which book(s) his story appears. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
