<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/866266-is-it-ever-explained-why-bran-hated-eamonn">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Is it ever explained why Bran hated Eamonn so much? He seemed to have something against Eamonn simply because Eamonn's father was a traitor. It seemed to me that if anyone was justified to hold a grudge in this book it was Eamonn. Bran killed his men, got the girl he was in love with, and hates his guts simply because he carries his father's genes...I am genuinely confused by this. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_866266'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13927.Son_of_the_Shadows">like</a></span>

